name: Instagram story backgrounds
description:
These frames could be used to add to your instagram story to add stickers and songs with a nice background instead of the default background or a not that good picture. 

It's unfortunately impossible to add posts and extern shares (spotify, soundcloud, deezer, etc.) to your story with a custom background, so please use the last frame for those and the Instagram music sticker in comination with the second frame.

Hope you have fun!

The font is redaction: https://www.redaction.us/
